item.title: Power-packed 'Yashoda' trailer has Telugu and Tamil film actress Samantha playing a surrogate mother
item.description: Power-packed ‘Yashoda’ trailer has Telugu and Tamil film actress Samantha playing a surrogate mother The trailer promises a sleek thriller with Samantha doing complete justice to her part as she fights, chases and never backs down in her fight in the film

item.title: Makers unveil Telugu film actor Prabhas' look from upcoming movie 'Salaar'
item.description: Makers unveil Telugu film actor Prabhas' look from upcoming movie ‘Salaar’ According to the makers, ‘Salaar’ is one of the most anticipated films, more so because of Prabhas as the lead actor as he enjoys a Pan-India appeal.
